  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2021-12-14",
    "date": "2022-06-06T14:49:42Z",
    "text": "National Instant Criminal Background Check System (NICS) Data Integrity Act of 2021\n\nThis bill modifies procedures for conducting firearms-related background checks through the national instant criminal background check system (NICS).\n\nSpecifically, the bill requires the NICS to retain records related to a firearms-related background check for as long as necessary to determine whether an individual is eligible to receive a firearm.\n\nAdditionally, the bill requires the NICS to query additional databases for relevant information, including the National Data Exchange, the Interstate Identification Index System, and the National Crime Information Center databases."
